How do you handle stress

I handle stress in several ways. First of all, I try to maintain a positive attitude, as it helps me stay focused and solution-oriented. I prioritize my tasks based on urgency and work requirements, which allows me to manage my time more effectively.
In addition, I make it a habit to plan ahead at the end of each week, so I have a clear idea of what needs to be done in the following days. This also helps me anticipate potential challenges and prepare for them in advance.
Finally, I believe that maintaining a healthy lifestyle plays an important role in managing stress. It helps me stay calm and think clearly, which enables me to handle pressure more effectively when it arises.

